Seahorse Spark docker image
===========================

The image contains Hadoop, Spark, python libraries and Session Executor - all requirements for
running SX inside a docker container.

Full image name - docker-repo.deepsense.codilime.com/tap/deepsense-spark-yarn:seahorse_on_tap-latest

1. Building the image

   $ docker build -t deepsense-spark-yarn .

2) Publish the image

   $ docker tag deepsense-spark-yarn docker-repo.deepsense.codilime.com/tap/deepsense-spark-yarn:seahorse_on_tap-latest
   $ docker push docker-repo.deepsense.codilime.com/tap/deepsense-spark-yarn:seahorse_on_tap-latest

3. Running the image

   $ docker run -h sandbox -d deepsense-spark-yarn
   $ docker run -it -p 8088:8088 -p 8042:8042 -p 4040:4040 -h sandbox deepsense-spark-yarn bash
